Package: solace-browser
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libssl3 (>= 3.0), libffi8
Maintainer: Solace AI <hello@solaceagi.com>
Homepage: https://solaceagi.com
Description: AI automation backend for Solace Browser
 Solace Browser is an AI-powered browser built for autonomous task execution.
 The Yinyang Server is the local backend that powers the sidebar,
 runs recipes, manages evidence chains, and connects to Solace Hub.
 .
 Features:
  - 34+ AI automation apps (Gmail, LinkedIn, Calendar, and more)
  - OAuth3-scoped task delegation with step-up auth
  - Hash-chained tamper-evident evidence vault
  - Local-first: your data stays on your machine
  - Listens on port 8888
